    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoy 60 well-crafted 3D jigsaw puzzles! Discover a nice collection of puzzles and relax. Let the soothing gameplay help you unwind and de-stress.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309150/extras/e35964e9dfb38bcdcc5e19d387fc9352.poster.avif?t=1751521444\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309150/extras/e35964e9dfb38bcdcc5e19d387fc9352.webm?t=1751521444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309150/extras/e35964e9dfb38bcdcc5e19d387fc9352.mp4?t=1751521444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also challenge yourself with 2 timing options: <strong>Rush</strong> and <strong>Insane</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you make it in time?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309150/extras/b9ff7dc18ab5dd149e7752c191039bd4.avif?t=1751521444\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309150/extras_big/b9ff7dc18ab5dd149e7752c191039bd4.avif?t=1751521444 width=800 height=212 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 60  levels with awesome images</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play timeless, or compose puzzles within 3 and 1 minute with the - RUSH and INSANE game modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Soft ambient music to keep you concentrated</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Smooth gameplay: drag tiles on a grid of dots to gather them into a puzzle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light &amp; Dark modes available</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309150/extras/fadc3c946853d499bd7260d2ff2197e2.avif?t=1751521444\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309150/extras_big/fadc3c946853d499bd7260d2ff2197e2.avif?t=1751521444 width=800 height=212 /></span></p>",
